                </div>
                <div class="ml-4">
                  <h3 class="text-white font-bold">Instagram</h3>
                  <p class="text-white/80 group-hover:text-white">@NFLBettingPros</p>
                </div>
                <div class="ml-auto text-white">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.586 4.586a2 2 0 112.828 2.828l-3 3a2 2 0 01-2.828 0 1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414 4 4 0 005.656 0l3-3a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.5 1.5a1 1 0 101.414 1.414l1.5-1.5zm-5 5a2 2 0 012.828 0 1 1 0 101.414-1.414 4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-3 3a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.5-1.5a1 1 0 10-1.414-1.414l-1.5 1.5a2 2 0 11-2.828-2.828l3-3z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </a>
              
              <a href="https://facebook.com/NFLBettingPros" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="group flex items-center bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 p-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 8h-3v4h3v12h5v-12h3.642l.358-4h-4v-1.667c0-.955.192-1.333 1.115-1.333h2.885v-5h-3.808c-3.596 0-5.192 1.583-5.192 4.615v3.385z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="ml-4">
                  <h3 class="text-white font-bold">Facebook</h3>
                  <p class="text-white/80 group-hover:text-white">/NFLBettingPros</p>
                </div>
                <div class="ml-auto text-white">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.586 4.586a2 2 0 112.828 2.828l-3 3a2 2 0 01-2.828 0 1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414 4 4 0 005.656 0l3-3a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.5 1.5a1 1 0 101.414 1.414l1.5-1.5zm-5 5a2 2 0 012.828 0 1 1 0 101.414-1.414 4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-3 3a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.5-1.5a1 1 0 10-1.414-1.414l-1.5 1.5a2 2 0 11-2.828-2.828l3-3z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-white/20">
            <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">
              Follow us for daily betting insights, expert analysis, and exclusive content from our team of NFL professionals.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Message Section -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden border border-gray-100">
        <div class="md:flex">
          <div class="md:w-2/5 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-blue-800 p-8 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="inline-block p-4 bg-white/10 rounded-full mb-6">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Need Help?</h3>
              <p class="text-white/90">
                Our experts are standing by to assist you with any NFL betting questions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-3/5 p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Send Us a Message</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
              Whether you're a seasoned bettor or just starting your journey, our team is here to provide you with the insights you need to succeed.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-primary flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3 w-3 text-white" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="ml-3 text-gray-700">Expert betting strategies and advice</p>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-primary flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3 w-3 text-white" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="ml-3 text-gray-700">Collaboration opportunities</p>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-primary flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3 w-3 text-white" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="ml-3 text-gray-700">Latest NFL betting insights</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-blue-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Ready to Elevate Your Betting Game?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Join thousands of bettors who trust NFL Betting Pros for expert insights and winning strategies.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/subscribe" class="px-8 py-4 bg-accent hover:bg-red-600 text-white font-bold rounded-lg shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300 ease-in-out">
          Get Expert Insights
        </a>
        <a href="/strategies" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 text-primary font-bold rounded-lg shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300 ease-in-out">
          Explore Strategies
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .bg-grid-pattern {
      background-image: 
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 20px 20px;
    }
  </style>
